 the EA Sports universe for the chance to win tokens and other benefits.</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Partnership with G2 Esports: G2 Esports adds its experience running esports competitions to the metaverse, giving users the chance to compete in and watch live esports events, all while earning tokens and incentives for their time and effort.</span></p><p> </p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Both Playhera and G2 Esports boast sizable and interactive fan bases; the former has 150,000 and the latter 12 million Twitch subscribers.</span></p>						</div>
